name: Bumshaft
description: Amidst the IBS token surge, a clank.fun meme emerged as a hero. Bumshaft, born as a playful twist on Dickbutt, has grown into a phenomenon. It's gearing up for an upcoming 3,333 PFP NFT collection that blends top-tier art, vibes, and a cute, friendly face adored by many. Offered as a free mint to active participants it aims to unite the clanker ecosystem, with ambitions to have thousands of Bumshaft PFPs across socials, showcasing the ecosystem's strength
